description: Seinfeld Genius is a fun trivia skill that gives users ability to test their knowledge about the TV show. Players can see what they really remember about Jerry, George, Elaine, Kramer, and the rest of the gang by answering multiple choice questions. Great for parties or solo play.
name: Seinfeld Genius
shortDescription: Are you a fan of Seinfeld? Then enable Seinfeld Genius and see how much you really know about the hilarious sitcom from the '90s!
